## EmbeddingManager

`EmbeddingManager` is decoupled from `KnowledgeGraph`. Construct it separately when
embeddings are needed; do not expect the graph to own one.

```rust
// Auto: reads LEMONADE_URL env var; errors clearly if not set
let mgr = EmbeddingManager::try_new_auto(None, None).await?;

// Explicit URL
let mgr = EmbeddingManager::try_new_lemonade(
    "http://localhost:8000/api/v1",
    "nomic-embed-text",
).await?;

let provider = mgr.get_provider();  // Arc<dyn EmbeddingProvider>
let vec = provider.embed("Some text").await?;
```

`try_new_auto` resolution order:
1. `lemonade_url` argument (if `Some`)
2. `LEMONADE_URL` environment variable
3. Hard error — there is **no** local fallback in this build

