## ObjectBuilder Pattern

Fluent API for constructing graph objects:

```rust
let id = ObjectBuilder::character("Gandalf".to_string())
    .with_description("A wise wizard".to_string())
    .with_property("race".to_string(), "Maiar".to_string())
    .with_json_property("level".to_string(), serde_json::json!(20))
    .with_tag("wizard".to_string())
    .add_to_graph(&graph)?;
```

Convenience constructors: `character`, `location`, `faction`, `item`, `event`,
`session`, `custom(type, name)`.

